{"tid":2491540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來有警嫂聽日結婚4周年","createTime":"2021-04-16T11:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T11:53:49.000Z","uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70282e1d6ac237cc7cfe7883e5f19ceccc049504","tid":2491540,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T11:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n原來噚日仲係April嘅大喜日子，佢同任職警務人員、姓鄧嘅總督察拉埋天窗，恭喜恭喜！一對新人下午喺小教堂行禮，晚上再於尖沙咀喜來登酒店舉行婚宴，一班無綫新聞部同事都有到賀，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">包括新聞部高層袁志偉、主播黃麗幗、陳嘉倩、羅鈺文及前無綫主播姚雋彥等，各人都喺社交網上分享喜悅，見佢哋影大合照時都笑容燦爛，非常熱鬧</span></span>。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20170418/DZAMEUMZCZFAG5OXOTHICTETKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20170418%2FDZAMEUMZCZFAG5OXOTHICTETKU%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=8c63234f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20170418%2FDZAMEUMZCZFAG5OXOTHICTETKU%2F&h=65599c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20170418/DZAMEUMZCZFAG5OXOTHICTETKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢老公 = O記 <span class=\"red\">鄧翊几</span> 警司<br />\n姐係以前跟開李桂華大導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年年尾先升警司<br />\n相信一定係打9班黑暴有功先有得升<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>去年6月12日大批示威者於金鐘衝突中被捕，其中一名年輕救生員早前承認一項暴動罪，案件今於區域法院判刑。22歲被告冼嘉豪，報稱任職救生員，被判監4年。警方表示，歡迎法庭裁決。<br />\n  <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察鄧翊几表示，警方對法庭裁決表示歡迎，認為判刑能反映暴動的嚴重程度，指裁決可以給社會反思機會。他指，案件以6年為量刑起點，充分反映暴動罪嚴重性。<br />\n </span></span> </blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmacYGpZgNntp6ENgVZU29FqmbraQsiGZXYwNucxX1y5Nb?filename=JtZmTY1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtZmTY1.png&h=ab856c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYv6rhdjHECYjsMtsyUfmZvzCSQFVaMp499gyQS6WC73e?filename=CUeuis9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l